-- Mothercare to Make 158 Non-Store Staff Redundant, Times Reports
-- B y   G a v i n   F i n c h
-- 2012-03-17T12:17:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-17/mothercare-to-make-158-non-store-staff-redundant-times-reports.html
Mothercare Plc (MTC)  is in talks with 158
non-store staff about making them redundant, the Times of  London 
reported, citing a company announcement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gavin Finch in London at 
